    <entry>
      <title>Flutter 与安卓原生通信</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/02/Flutter%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/02/Flutter%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在大部分Flutter开发的场景中，都不怎么需要写安卓原生相关的代码，很多涉及原生的功能通过添加三方库调用对应的方法即可实现，但为了对与原生交互有了解还是需要学习是怎么实现通信的。下面是一个简单的例子，使用<code>MethodChannel</code>来获取手机当前的电量，使用<code>EventChannel</code>来持续监听计时器的次数。</p><h2 id="Flutter-端代码（main-dart）"><a href="#Flutter-端代码（main-dart）" class="headerlink" title="Flutter 端代码（main.dart）"></a>Flutter 端代码（main.dart）</h2><h3 id="1-定义通道名称"><a href="#1-定义通道名称" class="headerlink" title="1. 定义通道名称"></a>1. 定义通道名称</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// lib/main.dart</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// MethodChannel 通道</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">const</span> _methodChannel = MethodChannel(<span class="string">&#x27;com.example.app/battery&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// EventChannel 通道</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">const</span> _eventChannel = EventChannel(<span class="string">&#x27;com.example.app/timer&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-定义变量"><a href="#2-定义变量" class="headerlink" title="2. 定义变量"></a>2. 定义变量</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// lib/main.dart</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">String</span> _batteryLevel = <span class="string">&#x27;未知&#x27;</span>; <span class="comment">// 电量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">int</span> _timerCount = <span class="number">0</span>; <span class="comment">// 计时器</span></span><br><span class="line">StreamSubscription? _timerSubscription; <span class="comment">// 订阅数据流</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-调用-MethodChannel-获取电量"><a href="#3-调用-MethodChannel-获取电量" class="headerlink" title="3. 调用 MethodChannel 获取电量"></a>3. 调用 MethodChannel 获取电量</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// lib/main.dart</span></span><br><span class="line">Future&lt;<span class="keyword">void</span>&gt; _getBatteryLevel() <span class="keyword">async</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">final</span> <span class="built_in">int</span> result = <span class="keyword">await</span> _methodChannel.invokeMethod(<span class="string">&#x27;getBatteryLevel&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    setState(() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      _batteryLevel = <span class="string">&quot;<span class="subst">$result</span>%&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125; <span class="keyword">on</span> PlatformException <span class="keyword">catch</span> (e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    setState(() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      _batteryLevel = <span class="string">&quot;获取失败: <span class="subst">$&#123;e.message&#125;</span>&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-调用-EventChannel-获取计时器值"><a href="#4-调用-EventChannel-获取计时器值" class="headerlink" title="4. 调用 EventChannel 获取计时器值"></a>4. 调用 EventChannel 获取计时器值</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// lib/main.dart</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> _startTimerListen() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  _timerSubscription?.cancel(); <span class="comment">// 取消之前的订阅</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 开始监听数据流</span></span><br><span class="line">  _timerSubscription = _eventChannel.receiveBroadcastStream().listen(</span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="built_in">dynamic</span> event) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      setState(() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        _timerCount = event <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="built_in">int</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    onError: (<span class="built_in">Object</span> error) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;收到错误: <span class="subst">$error</span>&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    onDone: () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;timer stream 已关闭&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-释放"><a href="#5-释放" class="headerlink" title="5. 释放"></a>5. 释放</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// lib/main.dart</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> dispose() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  _timerSubscription?.cancel();</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">super</span>.dispose();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Kotlin-代码（MainActivity-kt）"><a href="#Kotlin-代码（MainActivity-kt）" class="headerlink" title="Kotlin 代码（MainActivity.kt）"></a>Kotlin 代码（MainActivity.kt）</h2><p>在<code>MainActivity</code>类中的<code>override fun configureFlutterEngine(flutterEngine: FlutterEngine)</code>里写</p><h3 id="1-定义二进制信使"><a href="#1-定义二进制信使" class="headerlink" title="1. 定义二进制信使"></a>1. 定义二进制信使</h3><figure class="highlight kt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// MainActivity.kt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">val</span> messenger = flutterEngine.dartExecutor.binaryMessenger</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><strong>🔧 核心概念速查</strong></p><ul><li><strong><code>flutterEngine</code>（Flutter 引擎）</strong>：运行在安卓后台的”Flutter 大脑”，负责渲染 UI、管理内存以及运行 Dart 代码。</li><li><strong><code>dartExecutor</code>（Dart 执行器）</strong>：引擎中专门负责执行 Dart 代码的机构（可以理解为运行 Dart 的虚拟机入口）。</li><li><strong><code>binaryMessenger</code>（二进制信使）</strong>：最核心的通信工具，负责在 Dart 和 Kotlin 之间传递底层的二进制数据（<code>Byte</code>）。</li></ul></blockquote><hr><h3 id="🤔-为什么叫-binaryMessenger（二进制信使）？"><a href="#🤔-为什么叫-binaryMessenger（二进制信使）？" class="headerlink" title="🤔 为什么叫 binaryMessenger（二进制信使）？"></a>🤔 为什么叫 binaryMessenger（二进制信使）？</h3><p>Flutter 和安卓原生运行在<strong>两个不同的运行环境</strong>中 —— Kotlin 无法直接读取 Dart 的内存对象，Dart 也无法直接调用 Kotlin 的类。</p><p>它们之间唯一的交流方式，就像寄快递一样：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">步骤</th><th align="left">阶段</th><th align="left">说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><strong>① 打包</strong></td><td align="left">📦 序列化</td><td align="left">Flutter 把想发送的数据（比如字符串 <code>&quot;getBatteryLevel&quot;</code>）序列化成一串 <code>0</code> 和 <code>1</code> 的二进制字节流（Binary Bytes）</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><strong>② 运输</strong></td><td align="left">🚚 跨边界传递</td><td align="left"><code>binaryMessenger</code> 抬着这串字节流，跨越 C++ 底层边界，送到安卓原生这一侧</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><strong>③ 拆包</strong></td><td align="left">📬 反序列化</td><td align="left">安卓原生的 <code>MethodChannel</code> 收到字节流后，将其反序列化还原成 Kotlin 的 <code>String</code></td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p><strong>💡 一句话总结</strong></p><p>无论你创建的是 <code>MethodChannel</code> 还是 <code>EventChannel</code>，它们的构造函数<strong>第一个参数永远都需要传入 <code>binaryMessenger</code></strong>。<br>因为它才是底层真正干苦力、运送数据的”快递员”，而 Channel 只是套在它外面的一层”精装外壳”。</p></blockquote><h3 id="2-MethodChannel-方法实现"><a href="#2-MethodChannel-方法实现" class="headerlink" title="2. MethodChannel 方法实现"></a>2. MethodChannel 方法实现</h3><figure class="highlight kt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// MainActivity.kt</span></span><br><span class="line">MethodChannel(messenger, <span class="string">&quot;com.example.app/battery&quot;</span>).setMethodCallHandler &#123; call, result -&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 判断调用的是哪个方法</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (call.method == <span class="string">&quot;getBatteryLevel&quot;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">val</span> batteryLevel = getBatteryLevel()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (batteryLevel != -<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            result.success(batteryLevel)</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            result.error(<span class="string">&quot;Unavailable&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;无法获取电量&quot;</span>, <span class="literal">null</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        result.notImplemented()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-EventChannel-方法实现"><a href="#3-EventChannel-方法实现" class="headerlink" title="3. EventChannel 方法实现"></a>3. EventChannel 方法实现</h3><figure class="highlight kt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// MainActivity.kt</span></span><br><span class="line">EventChannel(messenger, <span class="string">&quot;com.example.app/timer&quot;</span>).setStreamHandler(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">object</span> : EventChannel.StreamHandler &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">val</span> handler = Handler(Looper.getMainLooper())</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">var</span> runnable: Runnable? = <span class="literal">null</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">var</span> count = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 当 Flutter 端开始 listen 监听时触发</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">override</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">onListen</span><span class="params">(arguments: <span class="type">Any</span>?, events: <span class="type">EventChannel</span>.<span class="type">EventSink</span>?)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            runnable = <span class="keyword">object</span> : Runnable &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">override</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    count++</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="comment">// 主动将数据推送给 Flutter</span></span><br><span class="line">                    events?.success(count)</span><br><span class="line">                    handler.postDelayed(<span class="keyword">this</span>, <span class="number">1000</span>) <span class="comment">// 每秒发送一次</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            handler.post(runnable!!)</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 当 Flutter 取消监听或销毁时触发</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">override</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">onCancel</span><span class="params">(arguments: <span class="type">Any</span>?)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            runnable?.let &#123; handler.removeCallbacks(it) &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            runnable = <span class="literal">null</span></span><br><span class="line">            count = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-获取电量方法"><a href="#4-获取电量方法" class="headerlink" title="4. 获取电量方法"></a>4. 获取电量方法</h3><p><code>MainActivity</code>类的方法</p><figure class="highlight kt"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// MainActivity.kt</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">getBatteryLevel</span><span class="params">()</span></span>: <span class="built_in">Int</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">val</span> batteryLevel: <span class="built_in">Int</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (Build.VERSION.SDK_INT &gt;= Build.VERSION_CODES.LOLLIPOP) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">val</span> batteryManager = getSystemService(Context.BATTERY_SERVICE) <span class="keyword">as</span> BatteryManager</span><br><span class="line">        batteryLevel = batteryManager.getIntProperty(BatteryManager.BATTERY_PROPERTY_CAPACITY)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">val</span> intent = ContextWrapper(applicationContext).registerReceiver(<span class="literal">null</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            IntentFilter(Intent.ACTION_BATTERY_CHANGED)</span><br><span class="line">        )</span><br><span class="line">        batteryLevel = intent!!.getIntExtra(BatteryManager.EXTRA_LEVEL, -<span class="number">1</span>) * <span class="number">100</span> / intent.getIntExtra(BatteryManager.EXTRA_SCALE, -<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> batteryLevel</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Flutter-端-UI-组件中使用"><a href="#Flutter-端-UI-组件中使用" class="headerlink" title="Flutter 端 UI 组件中使用"></a>Flutter 端 UI 组件中使用</h2><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line">Widget build(BuildContext context) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> Scaffold(</span><br><span class="line">    appBar: AppBar(title: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;Flutter &amp; Native&#x27;</span>)),</span><br><span class="line">    body: Center(</span><br><span class="line">      child: Column(</span><br><span class="line">        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,</span><br><span class="line">        children: [</span><br><span class="line">          Text(<span class="string">&#x27;当前手机电量：<span class="subst">$_batteryLevel</span>&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">const</span> SizedBox(height: <span class="number">20</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ElevatedButton(</span><br><span class="line">            onPressed: _getBatteryLevel,</span><br><span class="line">            child: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;获取电量&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ),</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">const</span> SizedBox(height: <span class="number">20</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          Text(<span class="string">&#x27;EventChannel 计时器：<span class="subst">$_timerCount</span>&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">const</span> SizedBox(height: <span class="number">20</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ElevatedButton(</span><br><span class="line">            onPressed: _startTimerListen,</span><br><span class="line">            child: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;开始监听&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ),</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">const</span> SizedBox(height: <span class="number">20</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ElevatedButton(</span><br><span class="line">            onPressed: () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              _timerSubscription?.cancel();</span><br><span class="line">              setState(() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                _timerCount = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                _timerSubscription = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            child: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;停止监听&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ),</span><br><span class="line">        ],</span><br><span class="line">      ),</span><br><span class="line">    ),</span><br><span class="line">  );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结与避坑指南"><a href="#总结与避坑指南" class="headerlink" title="总结与避坑指南"></a>总结与避坑指南</h2><h3 id="1-两种通道的核心对比"><a href="#1-两种通道的核心对比" class="headerlink" title="1. 两种通道的核心对比"></a>1. 两种通道的核心对比</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="left">通道类型</th><th align="left">通信模式</th><th align="left">适用场景</th><th align="left">类比</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><strong><code>MethodChannel</code></strong></td><td align="left"><strong>一问一答（单次请求）</strong></td><td align="left">获取电量、调用原生系统弹窗、获取系统版本等</td><td align="left">HTTP 请求</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><strong><code>EventChannel</code></strong></td><td align="left"><strong>单向持续推送（流式传输）</strong></td><td align="left">监听传感器数据、手机电量变化、蓝牙扫描、定时器等</td><td align="left">WebSocket &#x2F; 广播</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="2-生产环境避坑指南"><a href="#2-生产环境避坑指南" class="headerlink" title="2. 生产环境避坑指南"></a>2. 生产环境避坑指南</h3><p>在实际的商业项目开发中，使用原生通信需要特别注意以下几点：</p><ol><li><strong>通道命名规范（唯一性）：</strong><br>通道名称建议使用<strong>反向域名</strong>（如 <code>com.yourcompany.app/feature</code>）。如果两个通道重名，App 运行时会直接崩溃或发生严重的数据错乱。</li><li><strong>必须做好内存释放：</strong><br><code>EventChannel</code> 必须在 Flutter 的 <code>dispose()</code> 方法中调用 <code>cancel()</code> 取消订阅。如果忘记取消，即使页面关闭了，原生的定时器或监听器依然会驻留在内存中，导致<strong>内存泄漏</strong>。</li><li><strong>永远要用 <code>try-catch</code> 包裹调用：</strong><br>只要是跨端调用，就有可能因为原生报错、方法未实现等原因抛出 <code>PlatformException</code>。Flutter 端的调用必须用 <code>try-catch</code> 包裹，防止程序崩溃。</li><li><strong>原生端避免阻塞主线程：</strong><br>Kotlin 端的 <code>setMethodCallHandler</code> 默认运行在 <strong>Android 的 UI 主线程</strong>中。如果要在原生做耗时的 C++ 运算或网络请求，必须开辟子线程（如使用 Kotlin 协程），计算完毕后再切回主线程通过 <code>result.success</code> 返回结果，否则会导致界面卡死。</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Flutter </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Flutter </tag>
            
            <tag> Kotlin </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>C++智能指针</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/01/C-%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/01/C-%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>现代C++可以使用智能指针（Smart Pointers）来自动管理动态对象的生命周期（“召之即来，挥之即去”），减少因手动<code>new/delete</code>导致的资源泄露风险。Java&#x2F;Kotlin层与C++交互时主要使用JNI，JNI导出的函数本质上是Java与Native层之间的桥梁，Native层不会自动维护C++对象生命周期，因此通常需要在C++层保存对象实例。此时需要一个全局的、内存常驻的智能指针来管理。</p><h3 id="1-出生（实例化）"><a href="#1-出生（实例化）" class="headerlink" title="1.出生（实例化）"></a>1.出生（实例化）</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 定义全局智能指针</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">static</span> std::unique_ptr&lt;Live2DRenderer&gt; g_renderer;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 在方法里使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 如果之前有老的主角，先送他退场</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (g_renderer) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    g_renderer-&gt;<span class="built_in">Destroy</span>();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 实例化新主角！</span></span><br><span class="line">g_renderer = std::<span class="built_in">make_unique</span>&lt;Live2DRenderer&gt;();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>unique_ptr表示独占所有权（exclusive ownership），同一时间只能有一个指针拥有该对象。</p><h3 id="2-搬砖（执行中）"><a href="#2-搬砖（执行中）" class="headerlink" title="2.搬砖（执行中）"></a>2.搬砖（执行中）</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!g_renderer) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">g_renderer-&gt;<span class="built_in">PlayMotion</span>(...);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-退场（析构）"><a href="#3-退场（析构）" class="headerlink" title="3.退场（析构）"></a>3.退场（析构）</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (g_renderer) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    g_renderer-&gt;<span class="built_in">Destroy</span>(); <span class="comment">// 释放 OpenGL 和线程等资源</span></span><br><span class="line">    g_renderer.<span class="built_in">reset</span>();    <span class="comment">// 重置智能指针，自动销毁</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>析构函数体执行完毕后，C++运行时会自动按照声明顺序的<code>逆序</code>，逐个销毁类的成员变量。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> C++ </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C++ </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Riverpod 使用笔记</title>
      <link href="/2026/06/08/Flutter-Riverpod-Notes/"/>
      <url>/2026/06/08/Flutter-Riverpod-Notes/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Flutter中实现状态管理有很多方式，自带的有局限性，且全局管理较为复杂。而三方状态管理库，目前我使用过的有Provider、GetX和Riverpod。Provider比较基础和入门，GetX简单但是过于魔法，路由栈的管理有点乱（因为不需要<code>context</code>就能到处跳）。Riverpod则是Provider的升级版，网上的佬友们都说好，问AI哪个状态管理库好用，基本上都会推荐Riverpod，所以我也就入坑了，就是这样。</p><h3 id="1-安装依赖"><a href="#1-安装依赖" class="headerlink" title="1.安装依赖"></a>1.安装依赖</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">flutter_riverpod:</span> <span class="string">^3.0.3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-创建状态管理器"><a href="#2-创建状态管理器" class="headerlink" title="2.创建状态管理器"></a>2.创建状态管理器</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> lightMode = ThemeData(brightness: Brightness.light);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> darkMode = ThemeData(brightness: Brightness.dark);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">主题状态管理器</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ThemeNotifier</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">Notifier</span>&lt;<span class="title">ThemeData</span>&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line">  ThemeData build() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 默认使用暗色主题</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> darkMode;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">切换主题</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> toggleTheme() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    state = state.brightness == Brightness.light ? darkMode : lightMode;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">设置特定主题</span></span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> setTheme(ThemeData themeData) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    state = themeData;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-创建Provider"><a href="#3-创建Provider" class="headerlink" title="3.创建Provider"></a>3.创建Provider</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/// <span class="language-markdown">主题的 Provider</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">final</span> themeProvider = NotifierProvider&lt;ThemeNotifier, ThemeData&gt;(() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> ThemeNotifier();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-包裹main函数"><a href="#4-包裹main函数" class="headerlink" title="4.包裹main函数"></a>4.包裹<code>main</code>函数</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> main() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  runApp(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> ProviderScope(</span><br><span class="line">      child: MyApp(),</span><br><span class="line">    ),</span><br><span class="line">  );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-使用Provider"><a href="#5-使用Provider" class="headerlink" title="5.使用Provider"></a>5.使用Provider</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MyApp</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">ConsumerWidget</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> MyApp(&#123;<span class="keyword">super</span>.key&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line">  Widget build(BuildContext context, WidgetRef ref) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">final</span> themeData = ref.watch(themeProvider);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> MaterialApp(</span><br><span class="line">      theme: themeData,</span><br><span class="line">      home: Scaffold(</span><br><span class="line">        appBar: AppBar(title: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;Riverpod Theme Demo&#x27;</span>)),</span><br><span class="line">        body: Center(</span><br><span class="line">          child: ElevatedButton(</span><br><span class="line">            onPressed: () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="comment">// 修改主题状态</span></span><br><span class="line">              ref.read(themeProvider.notifier).toggleTheme();</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            child: <span class="keyword">const</span> Text(<span class="string">&#x27;切换主题&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">          ),</span><br><span class="line">        ),</span><br><span class="line">      ),</span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="补充"><a href="#补充" class="headerlink" title="补充"></a>补充</h3><p>Riverpod还可以直接生成代码，使用代码生成工具跑一下可以自动生成Provider，减少样板代码。这个我用的比较少🤗，后面再研究研究。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Flutter </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Flutter </tag>
            
            <tag> Riverpod </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>GoRoute 使用笔记</title>
      <link href="/2026/06/08/Flutter-GoRoute-Notes/"/>
      <url>/2026/06/08/Flutter-GoRoute-Notes/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在 Flutter 开发中，我们经常使用命令式路由（Navigator 1.0&#x2F;2.0），但在路由链路较深时会越来越麻烦。本文以 <strong>Lumi</strong> 项目为例，记录官方推荐的声明式路由库 <code>GoRouter</code> 的基础使用方式。</p><h3 id="1-添加依赖"><a href="#1-添加依赖" class="headerlink" title="1. 添加依赖"></a>1. 添加依赖</h3><p>首先，在项目根目录的 <code>pubspec.yaml</code> 文件中引入最新或稳定的 <code>go_router</code> 依赖：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">dependencies:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">go_router:</span> <span class="string">^17.0.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>💡 提示：添加完成后，在终端执行 <code>flutter pub get</code> 来刷新并下载依赖包。</p><h3 id="2-创建路由配置"><a href="#2-创建路由配置" class="headerlink" title="2.创建路由配置"></a>2.创建路由配置</h3><p>为了避免硬编码（Magic String）带来的维护灾难，建议将所有的路由 Path 统一抽取到 AppRoutes 抽象类中：</p><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">abstract</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">AppRoutes</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="built_in">String</span> home = <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="built_in">String</span> settings = <span class="string">&#x27;/settings&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  ... <span class="comment">// 其他路由路径</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-定义路由"><a href="#3-定义路由" class="headerlink" title="3.定义路由"></a>3.定义路由</h3><p>创建 GoRouter 实例，并在其中配置路由表和重定向逻辑：</p><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GoRouter createAppRouter(<span class="built_in">bool</span> <span class="built_in">Function</span>() isLoggedIn) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> GoRouter(</span><br><span class="line">        initialLocation: AppRoutes.home,</span><br><span class="line">        observers: [LumiHomePage.routeObserver],</span><br><span class="line">        redirect: (context, state) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            ... <span class="comment">// 根据登录状态重定向</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        routes: [</span><br><span class="line">            GoRoute(</span><br><span class="line">                path: AppRoutes.home,</span><br><span class="line">                builder: (context, state) =&gt; <span class="keyword">const</span> LumiHomePage(),</span><br><span class="line">            ),</span><br><span class="line">            ... <span class="comment">// 其他路由定义</span></span><br><span class="line">        ]</span><br><span class="line">    )</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-使用路由"><a href="#4-使用路由" class="headerlink" title="4.使用路由"></a>4.使用路由</h3><p>在应用入口（通常是 App 根 Widget）处初始化路由。</p><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// app.dart</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 初始化</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> initState() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">super</span>.initState();</span><br><span class="line">    _router = createAppRouter(() =&gt; ref.read(authProvider).isLoggedIn);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 释放</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> dispose() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    _router.dispose();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">super</span>.dispose();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Widget树中使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@override</span></span><br><span class="line">Widget build(BuildContext context) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> MaterialApp.router(</span><br><span class="line">        routerConfig: _router,</span><br><span class="line">        ... <span class="comment">// 其他配置</span></span><br><span class="line">    );</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-导航"><a href="#5-导航" class="headerlink" title="5.导航"></a>5.导航</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 🧭 方式 A：无痕替换当前路由栈（适合平级、Tab 切换或重定向）</span></span><br><span class="line">context.go(AppRoutes.settings);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 📌 方式 B：将新页面压入当前路由栈顶部（适合详情页，支持原生返回键），一般使用这个</span></span><br><span class="line">context.push(AppRoutes.settings);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="参数传递"><a href="#参数传递" class="headerlink" title="参数传递"></a>参数传递</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 带参数导航</span></span><br><span class="line">context.push(<span class="string">&#x27;/user/123&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 定义路由时使用占位符</span></span><br><span class="line">GoRoute(</span><br><span class="line">    path: <span class="string">&#x27;/user/:id&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    builder: (context, state) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">final</span> userId = state.params[<span class="string">&#x27;id&#x27;</span>]!;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> UserPage(userId: userId);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 也可以使用 query 参数</span></span><br><span class="line">context.push(<span class="string">&#x27;/search?query=flutter&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 获取：state.uri.queryParameters[&#x27;keyword&#x27;]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="嵌套路由"><a href="#嵌套路由" class="headerlink" title="嵌套路由"></a>嵌套路由</h3><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">GoRoute(</span><br><span class="line">    path: <span class="string">&#x27;/dashboard&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    builder: (context, state) =&gt; <span class="keyword">const</span> DashboardPage(),</span><br><span class="line">    routes: [</span><br><span class="line">        GoRoute(</span><br><span class="line">            path: <span class="string">&#x27;profile&#x27;</span>,  <span class="comment">// 实际路径是 /dashboard/profile</span></span><br><span class="line">            builder: (context, state) =&gt; <span class="keyword">const</span> ProfilePage(),</span><br><span class="line">        ),</span><br><span class="line">        GoRoute(</span><br><span class="line">            path: <span class="string">&#x27;settings&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            builder: (context, state) =&gt; <span class="keyword">const</span> SettingsPage(),</span><br><span class="line">        ),</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="⚠️-避坑指南（go-与-push-的本质区别）："><a href="#⚠️-避坑指南（go-与-push-的本质区别）：" class="headerlink" title="⚠️ 避坑指南（go 与 push 的本质区别）："></a>⚠️ 避坑指南（go 与 push 的本质区别）：</h3><p>context.go() 会重置路由树的层级结构（匹配声明的拓扑结构）。</p><p>context.push() 则是生硬地在当前栈顶盖上一层新页面。如果用错，可能会导致返回键（Back Button）的行为不符合预期。</p><h3 id="总结："><a href="#总结：" class="headerlink" title="总结："></a>总结：</h3><ul><li>GoRoute 提供了简洁的路由配置方式，支持嵌套路由和参数传递。</li><li>通过 redirect 可以实现基于状态的路由重定向，适合处理登录状态等场景。</li><li>结合 Riverpod 可以更方便地管理路由状态和依赖关系。</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
